title: Should we show some luv to low BRS Gotchis?
body: With the current emphasis on high BRS for rarity farming, majority of summoned Gotchis are above 450 BRS. Low BRS Gotchis are more scarce but not rewarded in any way. To balance things out, instead of having the extreme 2 ends of high BRS for 'Rarity Farming', perhaps we can introduce a separate leaderboard for 'Normie Farming' to reward Gotchis who strive to stay in the middle '50' score, adding another dimension to choosing wearables stats, choosing which Gotchi to summon/buy, and maybe more to come, in the Realm / Mini-games. Normies deserve some luv too!
choices: Yes, lets give normies some luv
